Dialogue: 0,0:15:44.69,0:15:45.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,发射
Dialogue: 0,0:15:51.78,0:15:52.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,DaCosta呢
Dialogue: 0,0:16:01.01,0:16:01.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,队长
Dialogue: 0,0:16:02.90,0:16:04.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,DaCosta去船尾舱门
Dialogue: 0,0:16:05.18,0:16:06.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,收容机体后 最大推力
Dialogue: 0,0:16:07.28,0:16:08.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,这家伙很快 能甩掉的
Dialogue: 0,0:16:09.73,0:16:13.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,什么 Eternal和阿斯兰吗
Dialogue: 0,0:16:15.47,0:16:16.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,接到了追击命令
Dialogue: 0,0:16:17.81,0:16:21.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那速度 这艘Vesalius现在怎么可能追上
Dialogue: 0,0:16:22.09,0:16:24.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,只有交给Jachin防卫部队了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:27.28,0:16:31.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,这真是杰作啊 萨拉议长阁下
Dialogue: 0,0:16:37.16,0:16:38.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好..好快
Dialogue: 0,0:16:42.03,0:16:44.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,阿斯兰 没事吧
Dialogue: 0,0:16:44.94,0:16:45.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,拉克丝?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:48.66,0:16:50.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,哟 初次见面
Dialogue: 0,0:16:50.64,0:16:52.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,欢迎来到歌姬的战舰
Dialogue: 0,0:16:52.64,0:16:54.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我是安德烈·巴特菲尔德
Dialogue: 0,0:17:09.38,0:17:11.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,前方出现M.S.部队 数量50
Dialogue: 0,0:17:12.52,0:17:16.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Jachin的部队吗 不来就怪了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:17.00,0:17:19.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,准备发射主炮 启动CIWS
Dialogue: 0,0:17:19.87,0:17:21.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,这艘船上有M.S.吗
Dialogue: 0,0:17:22.01,0:17:23.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不巧 刚好都不在
Dialogue: 0,0:17:24.14,0:17:27.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,这艘船是Justice和Freedom的专用支援舰
Dialogue: 0,0:17:28.96,0:17:31.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,请打开所有对外通讯频道
Dialogue: 0,0:17:32.31,0:17:33.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,拉..拉克丝?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:33.49,0:17:34.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,明白
Dialogue: 0,0:17:35.55,0:17:37.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我是拉克丝·克莱因
Dialogue: 0,0:17:38.13,0:17:40.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,因为期望的未来不同
Dialogue: 0,0:17:40.23,0:17:44.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我们成为了萨拉议长的敌人
Dialogue: 0,0:17:44.26,0:17:47.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,但我不想和你们交战
Dialogue: 0,0:17:47.98,0:17:49.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,请让飞船通过
Dialogue: 0,0:17:50.06,0:17:52.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,也请大家能再想一下
Dialogue: 0,0:17:52.55,0:17:58.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我们真正要与之战斗的是什么
Dialogue: 0,0:17:58.49,0:17:59.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,队长
Dialogue: 0,0:17:59.50,0:18:03.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不要被骗了 我们接到了攻击命令
Dialogue: 0,0:18:04.94,0:18:08.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,突然被这么问一定很困惑
Dialogue: 0,0:18:10.57,0:18:11.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,开始迎击
Dialogue: 0,0:18:20.57,0:18:22.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,请避免击中驾驶舱
Dialogue: 0,0:18:22.87,0:18:24.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,这太难了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:25.41,0:18:26.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,主炮 发射
Dialogue: 0,0:18:30.87,0:18:33.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Blue Alpha 5和Charlie 7出现6架GINN
Dialogue: 0,0:18:34.43,0:18:35.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,来了 对空
Dialogue: 0,0:18:50.71,0:18:52.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Blue Delta 12 又有4架GINN
Dialogue: 0,0:18:53.50,0:18:54.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,导弹接近
Dialogue: 0,0:18:57.83,0:18:59.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,迎击来不及了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:59.79,0:19:00.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,导弹要击中了
